er.com |language=en |access-date=September 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Dunham, Keenan\"|[[File:Keenan Dunham.jpg|120px]]<br />'''Keenan Dunham'''|| style=\"background:#48D1CC;\" |\n| {{dts|1981|7|16}}<br />(age {{age nts|1981|7|16}})<br />[[Myrtle Beach, South Carolina]]\n| '''Chair of the [[Horry County, South Carolina|Horry County]], [[South Carolina]] Libertarian Party'''<br />Candidate for President in [[2016 Libertarian Party presidential primaries|2016]]\n| [[File:Flag of South Carolina.svg|73px|border]]<br />[[South Carolina]]\n| {{Hs|2018-08-26}}<br />August 26, 2018<br />FEC Filing<ref name=\"DunhamFiles\">{{cite web |url=https://www.fec.gov/data/candidate/P00013284/?cycle=2020&election_full=true&tab=about-candidate |title=DUNHAM, KEENAN WALLACE Candidate For President |website=Fec.gov |access-date=January 7, 2020}}</ref>\n| data-sort-value=\"555\"| 555<br /><small>(1.37%)</small>\n| '''0'''\n| <ref>{{cite web |date=November 6, 2018 |url=https://think-liberty.com/candidates/keenan-wallace-dunham/ |title=Keenan Wallace Dunham Candidacy Press Release |website=Think-liberty.com |access-date=January 7, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Vohra, Arvin\"|[[File:Arvin Vohra on The Tatiana Show (cropped).jpg|120px]]<br />'''[[Arvin Vohra]]'''|| style=\"background:#1E90FF;\" |\n| {{dts|1979|5|9}}<br /> (age {{age nts|1979|5|9}})<br />[[Silver Spring, Maryland]]\n| '''Vice Chair of the [[Libertarian National Committee|LNC]]<br />(2014\u20132018)'''<br />Nominee for [[United States Senate|U.S. Senate]] from [[Maryland]] in [[2016 United States Senate election in Maryland|2016]] and [[2018 United States Senate election in Maryland|2018]]<br />Nominee for [[United States House of Representatives|U.S. representative]] from [[Maryland's 5th congressional district|MD-05]] in [[2012 United States House of Representatives elections in Maryland|2012]] and [[Maryland's 4th congressional district|MD-04]] in [[2014 United States House of Representatives elections