ube.com/watch?v=rUgsKbjnbHg |title=Ohio Libertarian Party Presidential Debate |date=June 14, 2019 |via=YouTube}}</ref>\n|-\n| 6 || July 13, 2019 || || VFW Post 529 \u2013 George Dilboy Post,<br />[[Somerville, Massachusetts]] || [[Libertarian Party of Massachusetts]] || rowspan=\"2\"|[[Matt Welch]] || <ref name=\"WelchDebate\">{{cite web |url=https://reason.com/2019/07/15/libertarian-presidential-candidates-prefer-each-other-over-justin-amash/ |title=Libertarian Presidential Candidates Prefer Each Other Over Justin Amash |date=July 15, 2019 |access-date=July 17, 2019 |author=Welch, Matt |work=[[Reason (magazine)|Reason]] |author-link=Matt Welch}}</ref>\n|-\n| 7 || November 2, 2019 || 7\u20139 pm|| [[Francis Marion University]],<br />[[Florence, South Carolina]] || [[Libertarian Party of South Carolina]] || <ref name=\"WelchDebate\" />\n|-\n| 8 || November 9, 2019 || 7\u20139 pm|| [[Olean High School]],<br />[[Olean, New York]] || [[Libertarian Party of New York#Listed local affiliates|Cattaraugus County Libertarian Party]] || James Weeks II, Daniel Donnelly, and Luke Wenke || <ref name=\"OleanDebate\">{{cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/events/884771585237934/ |via=Facebook |title=The Olean Libertarian Presidential Debate}}</ref>\n|-\n|9 ||January 11, 2020 || || Holiday Inn,<br />[[Concord, New Hampshire]] ||[[Libertarian Party of New Hampshire]] ||Daniel Fishman\n|<ref name=\"LPNHdebate\">{{cite web |url=https://my.lpnh.org/event/2020-lp-new-hampshire-annual-convention-2020-01-11/ |title=2020 LP New Hampshire Annual Convention |website=Libertarian Party of New Hampshire |language=en-US |access-date=2019-11-11}}</ref>\n|-\n| 10 || January 18, 2020 || || Douglasville Convention Center,<br />[[Douglasville, Georgia]] || [[Libertarian Party of Georgia]]|| Jessica Szilagyi ||<ref>{{cite web |url=https://lpgeorgia.com/2020-libertarian-state-convention/ |title=2020 Libertarian State Convention |website=Libertarian Party of Georgia}}</ref>\n|-\n| 11 || February 16, 20