53246209 |title=I had a nice conversation with Jacob Hornberger a couple of days ago and I have decided to join his campaign and support him for the Libertarian Party Presidential nomination. |date=December 7, 2019 |access-date=December 9, 2019 |via=Twitter.com}}</ref>\n* [[Thomas Woods|Tom Woods]], historian and author<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fFbqaTABz7U |title=Ep. 1540 The Horton/Woods Liberty Battle Plan |website=[[YouTube]]}}</ref>\n* Dave Smith, comedian and podcaster<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oBSMRIaCIWU |title=Part Of The Problem #514 \u2013 Revolution 2.0 With Scott Horton |website=[[YouTube]]}}</ref>\n\n;Organizations\n*Libertarian Party Mises Caucus<ref>{{cite web |url=https://thelibertyherald.com/2020/01/07/lp-mises-caucus-endorses-jacob-hornberger-for-the-libertarian-nomination-for-president/ |title=LP Mises Caucus Endorses Jacob Hornberger for the Libertarian Nomination for President |date=January 7, 2020 |work=The Liberty Herald |author=Bentley, Robert J. |access-date=January 7, 2020}}</ref>\n\n;Newspapers and other media\n* ''The Liberty Herald'', news media website<ref>{{cite web |url=https://thelibertyherald.com/2019/12/29/jacob-hornberger-is-the-right-choice-for-the-libertarian-party-and-america/ |title=Jacob Hornberger is the Right Choice for The Libertarian Party and America |date=December 29, 2019 |work=The Liberty Herald |author=Bentley, Robert J. |access-date=December 29, 2019}}</ref>\n}}\n\n{{Endorsements box\n| title = Jo Jorgensen\n| list =\n;Municipal officials\n* Chris Powell, member of the [[Bethany, Oklahoma]] city council and nominee for [[Governor of Oklahoma|Governor]] of [[Oklahoma]] in [[2018 Oklahoma gubernatorial election|2018]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/okcspowell/status/1228775925162160129 |title=I encourage you to join me in supporting Jo Jorgensen for President. |access-date=February 15, 2020 |via=Twitter.com}}</ref>\n\n;Party officials\n* [[Steve Dasbach]], 